contentrichtext.text: {{Wiktionary|XP}} '''XP''' may refer to: ==Computing== * [[Windows XP]], an operating system * [[Athlon XP]], a series of AMD microprocessors * [[Extreme programming]], a software development methodology * XP, a complexity class in [[parameterized complexity]] ==Other== * [[Chi Rho]], a Christian symbol * [[Experience point]], a unit of measurement in role-playing games * [[Xeroderma pigmentosum]], a genetic disorder * [[Xtra Airways]], by IATA code * XP, [[List of emoticons|an emoticon]] ==See also== *[[Microsoft Office XP]], a Microsoft Office version {{disambiguation}}
